00:11:55.460 --> 00:11:57.230 align:middle line:90%
is an inside job.

00:11:57.230 --> 00:12:00.470 align:middle line:84%
Viktor Frankl, who was
in a concentration camp,

00:12:00.470 --> 00:12:03.650 align:middle line:84%
