00:12:23.700 --> 00:12:26.330 align:middle line:84%
And what he pointed
out-- he was not a--

00:12:26.330 --> 00:12:28.550 align:middle line:84%
but he was Jewish, of
course, but he was not

00:12:28.550 --> 00:12:31.520 align:middle line:84%
an orthodox or
particularly believing Jew.

00:12:31.520 --> 00:12:34.760 align:middle line:84%
He had the experience of
God, the experience of love

00:12:34.760 --> 00:12:39.185 align:middle line:84%
in his life, and that experience
ensued throughout his life.

00:12:39.185 --> 00:12:40.280 align:middle line:90%
