00:13:06.770 --> 00:13:09.440 align:middle line:84%
for anybody to be
an atheist today.

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:12.800 align:middle line:84%
To say you're an atheist
is a misunderstanding.

00:13:12.800 --> 00:13:15.800 align:middle line:84%
Even the logical positivists
were not atheists.

00:13:15.800 --> 00:13:17.050 align:middle line:90%
